text: Here is your opportunity to own a 2.5 acre mountain A-frame in the heart of the North Cascades. This 2 bedroom-2 Bathroom home can be used as residential or investment property. The interior has been thoughtfully designed and updated with a full kitchen, and many custom touches throughout. It is close to North Cascades National Park, with hiking opportunities right from the property. The land is surrounded by National Forest Service with Sutter Creek running through the property. There is a covered hot tub, two large decks and firepit. There is a year round dome on the property and designated camping spots for additional rental possibilities. The home is turn key ready and includes all furnishing.

Nestled in the foothills of Alger, your private escape awaits. Located in a storybook setting, this charming cottage is the perfect place to relax and unwind. Designed with the entertainer in mind, the open kitchen and adjoining dining room create a welcoming place to gather. Wander out through the french doors to the covered patio space, where conversations are long, and memories are made. Above the garage is base camp, a finished-out space that can flex as office space, an additional guest room or exercise space; catered to your specific needs. The detached studio makes a great bed shed, adding sleeping space for guests. There is a separate septic system, power & well servicing the manufactured home, which will be removed before closing.

Hard to find affordable home in Anacortes! Vista Too is a 55 plus community w/ no land or lot lease. Nestled against a greenbelt, this home offers peaceful and manageable indoor & outdoor living space. Super comfy 2 bedroom, one full bathroom w/ numerous updates that add great value: NEW ROOF in 2021, newer H20 tank, newer washer & dryer, updated bathroom & kitchen, newer windows and sills plus easy care laminate floors. Other great features: Driveway with carport, garden shed, 10 x 12 workshop with electricity plus a fully fenced backyard for your furry friend (s). Community RV parking too. Proximity to the Senior Center, walking trails & essential shopping & medical facilities, make this location very convenient. This one is worth a look!

Welcome to your dream home in the peaceful countryside! This spacious 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom manufactured home offers 1, 512 sq ft of comfortable living space, perfect for those who love to entertain. Step inside to a bright, open floor plan. The master suite boasts a large bathroom and a walk-in closet. The second family room, located off the kitchen and dining area, features a cozy fireplace. Outside, the large deck is ideal for summer gatherings. Enjoy stunning mountain views while you barbecue, gather around the firepit, or garden. This move-in ready home offers plenty of space both inside and out for all your needs. Don't waitthis charming home won't last long! Embrace the tranquility of country living today.

SECURE, GATED 55+ COMMUNITY! Well-kept, cute as a button home bursting w/ natural light & copious space. New appliances in 2020. Oversized kitchen island & pantry plus large skylight make the kitchen paradise. Open concept plan flows from spacious dining to bonus lounge room- perfect for gatherings. Game night in the XL living room or your pick of 2 covered porches. Enjoy evenings in privacy-focused backyard & listen to the brook flowing along greenbelt. Added bonuses: community events, privacy carport, 5-min drive to grocery store & hospital. 8X16 shed offers ample storage-new roof. Upgraded shower &blinds in primary, new coils in furnace, new blower in fireplace in 2024.

What an amazing opportunity to own this spectacular 1.8 acre home w/ a serene setting, quietly tucked away in gated Fidalgo Bay Estates community. Incredible indoor/outdoor entertaining- private backyard backs against forest lands Plus views of Mt Baker peer through the Eastern views. A lovely interior w/ hardwood floors, picturesque windows, abundance of natural light, & stone fireplace. Impressive floor plan- nearly 3300 sf, office, 4 spacious bedrooms, formal dining room, lg open living area. Gourmet kitchen features granite counters, stainless appl + gourmet chefs oven. Main level owners suite. Escape downstairs to the bonus room, bedroom four, and large storage area. Trail from the cul de sac goes to Whistle Lake & trails.
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Great location! Located on a cul-de-sac, seconds away from Bakerview Park and only minutes from I-5 and downtown MV. Front door opens to an open concept floorplan and vaulted ceilings. Great natural lighting all throughout home & double pane storm windows. Kitchen features a walk-in pantry and great storage all throughout. Home features a utility room that connects with a 3/4 walk-in bathtub. Spacious primary bedroom adjoins full bath. Sizeable guest bedroom located directly across from 3/4 bathroom. 360 sq ft garage features a workbench, storage shelves, and backyard access to a concrete patio for entertaining.

Welcome to Your New Home in a Friendly Adult (over 21) Community! Discover this better-than-new, light and bright, one-level home. Enjoy vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace in this spacious, open floor plan. Fully equipped with all the extras you wont find in new construction; you will enjoy a seamless move-in experience with these included features: Professional-grade refrigerator. Washer and brand-new dryer. HOA assessment for new build purchase already paid. Custom closet systems in all bedrooms. Elevated, mounted garage shelving. Installed window blinds. Maintenance-free living with landscaping provided. Youll love this vibrant community with its social events and active lifestyle options. Dont miss out on this move-in-ready gem!

Bring Your RV or Tiny Home to this cleared and level Cape Horn vacant lot. All the hard work has been completed: Septic, Water and Power are all installed on the property. This lot is zoned for year round recreational use but is in the Skagit River Floodway so Skagit County will not authorize a building permit. (Buyer to verify.) River Access is just a block away at the community park. Bask on the sandy beach at Cape Horn and enjoy your own private camping retreat, all set up and ready to go.

Nestled in the quiet Dewey Beach community, this stunning water view home offers a rare opportunity for luxury coastal living. Boasting panoramic southern views of the sparking waters of Similk Bay, every day feels like a vacation here. Main floor offers a spacious open floorplan, featuring a floor to ceiling river rock fireplace, soaring ceilings, gourmet kitchen w/walk-in pantry. Expansive deck is perfect for al fresco dining or simply relaxing. Primary suite offers breathtaking water views, a luxurious en-suite bath, and spacious walk-in closet. Walk-out bottom floor has massive family room, two huge storage rooms, separate bedroom and full bathroom, perfect for guests. Beautiful irrigated yard w/firepit for summer evening enjoyment.

What an incredible opportunity to own a home in the amazing neighborhood of the Hilltop Haven Community. Bring your tool belt and vision and restore this home to its original beauty. With four bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this 1, 800+ SQ FT home sits on a nearly 1/3 acre lot. The private backyard is flat, usable, and fenced. The large primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and private bath. The living room has a fireplace. There is an oversized attached two-car garage. RV parking is available alongside the home. Close to Medical care, shopping, restaurants, and other amenities. Cash only, the house is sold as is where it is without warranties.

Back on MARKET! Uncover the hidden glamour of this turn of the century 2 bedroom(Roughed) bath home! This is a fixer-upper and great opportunity to build equity and put your own touches into the project! Tiny home with so much potential. Seller has completed study for replacing foundation. Located in the town of Concrete! House is in rough condition, but with a little creativity and open mind this home can be brought back to its original beauty. Utilities are already in! This is sold AS IS . Seller has limited knowledge of the property and offers no warranties. Buyer to verify all information to their satisfaction. Motivated Seller! Close commute to Janicki Industries Bring your offers!

REFRESHED MID-CENTURY CHARMER paired with modern updates gives this home a cool vibe! ONE LEVEL and move in ready! NEW custom sized windows, vinyl plank floors, fresh interior paint & updated bathroom really make this home shine. The spacious double lot & mostly fenced yard offer plenty of room for vehicles, gardening & outdoor activities. New covered front porch & back deck add extra appeal too. The oversized one car garage, with new cement planked siding and exterior paint, is a versatile space for parking, storage or a workshop. This home's location is a major plus! Half a block to Maiben Park and the Senior Center. Schools, shopping & medical facilities are super close too. Minutes to HWY 20 and I-5. NO HOA. Bring the RV and boat!

Step into timeless charm with this beautifully updated 100+ year-old farmhouse! Nestled on a spacious 0.75-acre lot, this 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath gem offers the perfect blend of historic character and modern convenience. Enjoy the newly updated kitchen and dining area, fresh exterior paint, and the ease of main level living. The expansive, partially-fenced yard features fruit trees, an RV pad with hookups (its own private septic system), and a 2-car detached garage. 2nd floor bedrooms offer an area for the diy'er to dabble and create unique spaces -as they are a blank canvas. Located close to schools, shopping, dining, and I-5, this home boasts stunning territorial views of farmlandtruly a serene retreat, minutes from everything.

Welcome home to this serene 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom retreat in Mount Vernon, WA. This elegant home captures abundant natural light, creating a tranquil ambiance that invites relaxation. With its peaceful interior & timeless charm, this property offers a graceful blend of comfort & sophistication. This turnkey home features a fully fenced front & rear yard, perfect for enjoying long summer days & sunshine. Additionally, it offers ample storage, catering to your practical needs. Conveniently located with easy access to I-5 and all that Skagit Valley offers, including hospitals and schools. Walking distance to Mount Vernon's downtown area with an array of attractions, & nearby Little Mountain offers hiking/biking trails for outdoor enthusiasts.

If you're looking for tree house living on the hill in La Conner, come visit. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath well-maintained home offers 2, 344 SF of comfortable living along with 628 SF of garage and workshop. With trees to the east and south, Swinomish channel views to the north, and magical farm and mountain views to the east, you won't want to leave once you step inside. The kitchen boasts newly remodeled and upgraded stainless steel appliances, countertops and cabinets. Don't miss the unique Murphy bed in the SW bedroom that allows for a quick conversion between the office and guest room. It is secluded, but only a short walk to La Conner's quality shops, galleries and dining. A pre-inspection has been completed and is available.

NEW CONSTRUCTION! Home was under construction when first listed now completed March 2024. Quality construction in this amazing Keystone Building Services home. Main level living with an open concept layout offering views of Guemes Channel & San Juan Isl. Inviting stylish kitchen boasts high-end appliances & walk-in pantry w/built-ins. Step onto the partially covered deck with overhead heaters for seamless indoor/outdoor living. The main level features an office, powder rm, laundry & classy primary bdrm with deck access & spacious en-suite w/heated floors. Upstairs, large family rm with fireplace, full bth & 3 bdrms await. Plus enjoy wired electric car charger. Nestled near Anacortes Forestlands, San Juan Isl Ferry, & town amenities.

Perfect home and great neighborhood that you will love! Stunning views of Mt Baker from every room upstairs. 3 bedroom, 2.5 baths & 2 car garage. 3rd garage is for a smaller car, motorcycles or all your toys. Formal living and dining add to this beautiful home. May 2022 - Luxury Vinyl flooring installed & freshly painted entire main floor plus new water heater with 6 yr warranty. Wrap around covered deck and a gazebo in this enjoyable back yard. Enjoy the quiet while you BBQ or just relax. Gazebo has hot tub hook up ready for your hot tub to be installed. Walk out your back gate to a paved pathway that runs thru the neighborhood and meets up with more trails for your walking enjoyment. You will love this house and location!

Northwest hidden gem with no ferry needed! Remodeled from roof to crawl space, this single-story home boasts fresh open spaces w/lots of natural light. Primary BR w/ensuite offers luxurious wet sauna, jacuzzi & walk-in closet. The nearly 2.5 acres of fully fenced property feels like your own private oasis. With RV & boat space, heated greenhouse, raised garden beds, orchard & gazebo, enjoy year-round activities. New 40x40 shop, a mechanics dream w/tons of storage & 10k lb BendPak lift included. Samish Island will WOW you with its community events, beach access, trails, athletic courts & playground. Shopping/dining only 15mins away, making this location ideal for quiet living but suited for convenience.

Seize the chance to own this 6-plex in the heart of Mount Vernon. All units are currently leased, providing you with immediate rental income & stress-free investment. New roof in 2023. Each unit is 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, approx. 800 sq. ft. Tenants enjoy the convenience of an on-site laundry facility (possibility for additional income) With a solid 5.6% cap rate, this property is a strong addition to any investment portfolio. Whether youre an experienced investor aiming to diversify or newcomer seeking reliable entry into the market, this 6-plex combines stability with growth potential. Located near Skagit Valley Hospital, Mount Vernon HS, parks, shopping, & more, this property is perfectly positioned to attract & retain quality tenants

Looking for multi-generation living? How about 66 private, 180 degree, view acres with several dwellings. Custom built rambler with finished daylite bsmnt has partial kitchen, living area, 2 bdrms & 3/4 bath. Main level with open area of living, dining & beautifully remodeled kitchen w/walk in pantry. Lrg utility area with 3/4 bath & office. Primary bdrm has walk in closet & full bath. Large deck & windows across front of house so every room has stunning view. Lrg 2 car garage. Newer barn with 3130 sq ft & main level 920 sq ft ADU with 1 bedrm, 3/4 bath, 1/2 bath & utility rm. Huge RV storage area, very large storage area & 2 way garage. 1400 finished sq ft on upper level with 4 finished rms & 1 3/4 baths. DEVELOPMENT possibilities!

Charming Mid-Century single-level home on nearly half an acre in town! Featuring a newer membrane roof and thoughtful updates throughout, this home retains its original character. The spacious layout offers a primary suite with en-suite bath, plus two additional bedrooms with a full hall bath. Enjoy the privacy of mature trees while being conveniently close to town, medical facilities, and I-5. The living room boasts a beautiful beamed ceiling, and the cozy family room, with a wood stove and wood accents, opens to the backyardperfect for entertaining. Plenty of space for gardening, plus a versatile storage room and shed. A true must-see!

Welcome to your new home! This spacious, light-filled home offers 1, 354 sqft on the main floor, with 3 bedrooms & 1 baths. Nestled on a sunny, level .32-acre lot, the home flows seamlessly from a generous living room with a cozy wood-burning fireplace to a kitchen with an eating area. The bedrooms are large and inviting, complemented by a full bath. Downstairs, find an add'l 1, 158 sqft in the roughed-in basement, including a bath, ready for your vision. The home also features a 1-car attached garage. Outside, enjoy a fully fenced backyard with RV parking. Enjoy being close to restaurants, schools, & downtown activities, w/ easy freeway access. This home has it alldont let this fantastic opportunity pass you by!

Impeccably maintained and ready for you to move right in, this home boasts beautiful landscaping & hardscaping, complete with privacy shrubs & a fully fenced yard for peace of mind. Inside, the vaulted ceiling living room welcomes you with a cozy gas fireplace, while the spacious kitchen features walnut-colored cabinetry, a built-in buffet, & ample eat-in space. Bedrooms are generously sized, & the updated bathrooms add a touch of modern comfort. Bonus features include a newer roof, updated appliances, & a convenient garden shed with extended covered ports, complemented by a charming paver patio. This home is a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. Home is located outside of the 100-year flood zone. No flood insurance required.

Walking trails, parks, playgrounds and views in sought after Skagit Highlands! Possible assumption of 3.375% VA mortgage. 3 BR 2.5 BA home. Generous front porch and built in shelving in the entryway invites you to an open living area and kitchen. Granite counters, SS appliances, and a large island, perfect for entertaining. Dine area, BA, and walk in pantry leads to the 2 car garage. Second living area or office upstairs. 2 spacious BR with full BA. Primary BR with walk in closet (California Closet organizers in all closets!) and 5-piece bath including large soaking tub. Newer washer and dryer stays. Fully fenced yard. Easy drive to I-5, yet tucked away in the peaceful hills. Playground at the end of the street. This house has it all!

Step back in time to Grandma's house in this lovingly maintained, vintage mid-century home situated in peaceful setting walkable to the park, baseball & soccer fields, playground & Community Forest Land Trails. This treasured gem has been enjoyed by several generations. If the walls could only talk! It offers a convenient kitchen, cozy family room, living room, warm dining space for hosting holiday dinners. 1020 SF detached garage/shop space with power. Fenced yard, fruit tree and lots of mature plantings in the garden all on shy 15, 000 SF lot. Newer roof, leaf guards for gutters. New 200 amp electrical panel. Structural supports in the crawl space being addressed by contractor will be complete prior to closing. So many possibilities!

Beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath 1990 Redman doublewide (28 x 56) manufactured home with lovely kitchen and lots of cabinetry; separate laundry room; primary bedroom offers amazing bath suite with full walk in shower; second bath also beautifully remodeled. Wood laminate flooring. Buyer may select carpeting or wood laminate for each of three bedrooms. Great deck along southerly side of home; back porch; small storage building. Nice landscaping. 55+ community. Space rent is $730 per month plus garbage and water. (Garbage and water is approximately an extra $70 a month).

Enjoy luxurious living in desirable Bow with this majestic home on 2+ acres. No detail has been missed with extensive high-end updates. This custom home was designed with vaulted ceilings & huge windows to take in westerly views of the bay & spectacular sunsets. The main floor primary suite is like no other, with private access to the deck, sauna, steam shower, soaker tub, double vanities, and closetsall finished in marble. The airy kitchen is open to a sunroom and outdoor deck. Downstairs, find a family room/gym, safe room, new laundry, & 2 large bedrooms/bathsall in marble. In addition, a 3-car garage with cabinets & workbench. The peaceful, professionally landscaped property has an orchard, fenced garden, & community tennis courts!

Escape to tranquility in this delightful 1 bed/1bath cabin, perfectly nestled on 13.9 acres of pristine wilderness near Day Creek. Whether youre looking for a serene weekend retreat, a private getaway, or a cozy home surrounded by nature, this property offers it all. Cabin is currently down to the studs and is awaiting your personal touches. Surrounded by lush trees and vibrant greenery, this property is your gateway to the great outdoors. Enjoy morning coffee on the deck while listening to birdsong, or explore the surrounding forest. Visit local farm stands and enjoy the close proximity to the Skagit River. This property has been has been loved by the same family for over 50 years!

Over three acres of property in a great location! This property has a building permit in process. Well is in, septic is in, and the permitting process is nearly complete. Property has a nice pond on it; depending on your new home's location, you could have a view of the pond. This property is only one of two properties on this private road and it is surrounded by fields which gives you a private setting. There is an old single wide on the property. No restrictions on this property and no HOA. Manufactured homes OK.

Step into the world of Easy Street Cottages an intersection of convenience and charm! Nestled in the heart of Anacortes, the gateway to the San Juan Islands, our BRAND NEW cottages provide a flawless blend of contemporary living and quick access to parks, schools, shopping, picturesque trails, beaches, marinas, and the enchanting San Juan Islands. Project has preliminary plat approval.

Experience tranquility and privacy in the LIKE NEW Single Level Home surrounded by acres of protected greenbelt. Builders last and favorite lot. Step out your front door to a beautiful, treed trail for long walks. This lightly lived in home sits on a large corner lot, next to the serene park. Home boasts quarts countertops, HUGE center Island for entertaining, High-end appliances, vaulted ceilings, walk-in-closets and pantry. lovely utility room. Enjoy the primary suite with spa bath vessel tub all overlooking your fully fenced backyard and greenbelt. 3 Bed PLUS den with barn door. This home soars with natural light and is energy efficient. Highly sought after newer neighborhood. Close to all amenities, parks and trails. A home to brag about.

Step into the world of Easy Street Cottages an intersection of convenience and charm! Nestled in the heart of Anacortes, the gateway to the San Juan Islands, our BRAND NEW cottages provide a flawless blend of contemporary living and quick access to parks, schools, shopping, picturesque trails, beaches, marinas, and the enchanting San Juan Islands. Welcome to the Montreux 55+ community and this charming 3-bedroom home that exudes comfort and style. Step inside to discover the warm ambiance of hardwood floors throughout and a spacious primary suite complete with a full bath, ensuring a private and serene retreat. The heart of the home features granite countertops that complement the modern kitchen. Entertain with ease on the expansive patio, firepit, low maintenance yard, or enjoy evenings in the cozy great room. This residence also boasts a convenient 3-car garage and is ideally situated near the community park, offering ample opportunities for outdoor activities. With central air conditioning to keep you cool during the summer, this home is a haven of relaxation and convenience.

Brand New Community Bay View in the Burlington Country Club Area. Home will be complete Sept 10th. The plan features 1888 sq ft with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Island Kitchen opens to Great Room, dining area. Primary Bedroom with Large 5 piece Bath, stand alone tub, walk-in shower and walk-in closet. 3 additional Bedrooms up. Large back patio and covered front porch. Bay View schools. Next to Skagit Golf and Country Club, Edison, Chuckanut, La Conner and Anacortes. Shopping and I-5 minutes away. Special Financing options when working with the Preferred Lender. Buyers are able to customize finishes at the Design Center. For GPS use 16850 Peterson Road.

Come and see this lovely 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom 1994 double-wide manufactured home on a full acre of flat, mostly open, usable land. There is plenty of room to be private, enjoy seclusion, yet close enough to be in town in about 20 minutes. There is a single car garage with a shop built in as well. Plenty of room for hobby work. With this home nearly at the end of a dead end street, you won't suffer the sound of cars rushing by. This home and land are quiet, spacious, and peaceful. Definitely a place you can unwind from the stresses of everyday life. There are mature trees as well as many bushes, grass, and shrubs. The home is features a kitchen, living room, and dining room that all make up on big great room feel. Don't miss out!

Incredible updated home with main level living on 8.49 acres plus a massive shop for all your hobbies. This 2, 002 sqft home has been meticulously maintained & updated. Main level with gorgeous kitchen including Quartz countertops, custom cabinetry, large island & tile floors. Living room with gorgeous hardwood floors, a pellet stove to keep you cozy in the winter plus a mini-split heat pump for heating & A/C. Spacious primary bedroom on main level with 2 closets, walk in shower & two vanities. Upstairs with two large rooms plus full bathroom. Landing area for office/playroom. 2 car detached garage plus a 4, 200 sq ft shop with metal roof, 6 standard doors plus a 13' RV door. Level acreage & access to Nookachamps Creek. Extensive landscaping.

Welcome to this beautiful three-bedroom home in the Skagit Highlands! The inviting main floor layout features a cozy living room with a fireplace, a well-equipped kitchen with ample storage and a spacious island, a dining room, a convenient laundry room, and a half bath. Upstairs, you'll find a large primary suite with a luxurious 5-piece ensuite bath and an expansive walk-in closet. A good-sized loft, two additional bedrooms, and a full bath complete the upper level. The amazing fully fenced outdoor space is perfect for entertaining, boasting a covered patio, hot tub, and dog run. Enjoy easy access to I-5 and WA-9, as well as nearby parks and trails. Dont miss the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours!

{Turn Key 3 Bed/2 Bath Home w/Large Lot & Fenced Backyard!}This home has it all. Enter through the covered porch entrance into an open concept living area that flows into the kitchen. Both kitchen & living area have lots of natural lighting. Enjoy the breakfast nook or step out your sliding glass door into the huge backyard that is level & fully fenced. Backyard provides ample space for entertaining, gardening or just relaxation. Nice sized primary w/primary bath. Ideally located near shopping, restaurants, medical, interstate & much more. Fresh paint throughout the inside w/nice stainless appliances that all stay! This home is in great condition & ready for its' next owner. Come see it before it's gone.

Discover your dream home in the quiet gated community of Creekside Village. This low-maintenance 3-bedroom rambler is nestled on a private lot, offering serene views of the creek & woods. The inviting covered front porch leads to a great room w/vaulted ceilings, gas fp, oversized windows & dining space. Enjoy cooking in the spacious kitchen w/double oven, ample storage space & breakfast nook. Retreat to the primary bedrm w/en-suite bath & walk-in closet. Relax on the private deck. With a 2-car garage & all appliances included, this home is move-in ready. HOA covers exterior maintenance, yard care & road upkeep. The complex also offers RV parking possibilities. Conveniently located near Fidalgo pool, senior center, schools & all amenities.

Brand New Community Bay View under construction in the Burlington Country Club Area. The plan features 1888 sq ft with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Kitchen Island opens to Great Room, dining area. Primary Bedroom with Large 5 piece Bath and walk-in closet upstairs with 3 other Bedrooms. Large back patio and covered front porch. Bay View schools. Close to Skagit Country Club, Edison, Chuckanut, La Conner and Anacortes. Shopping a short distance away. Home to be complete mid September. Special Financing options when working with the Preferred Lender. Buyers are able to customize finishes at the Design Center. For GPS: 16850 Peterson Road.

Beautifully remodeled in 2016, this 1, 195 sq. ft home features 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bath, blending modern upgrades with timeless charm for cozy living. Freshly painted interior and exterior. Step into the open concept living room and spacious kitchen with eating bar, updated appliances and granite countertops. New electrical, plumbing, insulation, water heater and roof were installed at the time of remodel. New sewer line was replaced in 2022. Spacious two-car garage/shop with built-in storage shelves, plus an additional parking space. Move in ready and waiting for your personal touch. Just minutes away from schools, shopping, dining and local amenities.

Envision the good life here! Immaculately kept country setting home with partial view of Skagit River from the living area. Cozy wood stove. Entrance fully covered to keep out the rain. Covered rear entryway. 3bedroom , 2 full bathrooms, master has soaking tub & shower. Open concept design, kitchen has plenty of cabinet space with skylight providing ample light. Close to half acre, well maintained & fully fenced. Landscaped backyard, fruit trees, berry bushes & plenty of space for gardening. Detached carport & an additional shop for storage. Turn keycomes with all appliances washer/ dryer/ small freezer & furnishings. Sold as is.
